DVWA & OWASP Juice Shop

Description:
These applications provide a lightweight, safe playground for learning web-app security, testing scanners, and practicing exploitation techniques. Includes Damn Vulnerable Web App (DVWA) and OWASP Juice Shop. For training only — never expose these to production or the public internet.

What’s included

DVWA — classic PHP/MySQL vulnerable app for learning common web flaws (SQLi, XSS, CSRF, file upload, etc.).
OWASP Juice Shop — modern intentionally vulnerable Node.js app that covers a broad range of vulnerabilities and challenge-based learning.


Quick start

DVWA
1. Clone these repos:
  -  git clone https://github.com/digininja/DVWA.git

Juice-Shop
1. Clone these repos:
  -  git clone https://github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop.gitkali

